column12: I can't believe how well my sister's body holds up...
Kinda...hard to move...when you're just a head.
I can't wait to see them again!
But before that can happen, there's some stuff I gotta do first.
Like finding a body! Or at least some legs.
I sure hope Kainé and Weiss haven't killed each other yet.<LF>I swear, you leave 'em alone for one minute...
